msgstr "Floor plan — occupancy"

#: model:mail.template,subject:workinglocal_rental.mail_template_rental_contract_activated
msgid "Welkom — je huurcontract {{ object.name }} is actief"
msgstr "Welcome — your rental contract {{ object.name }} is active"

#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:workinglocal_rental.website_floorplan
msgid ""
"Zone-posities zijn een benadering op basis van de originele plannen\n"
"                            (LHOAS &amp; LHOAS architecten) — geen architecturaal-exacte trace.\n"
"                            Klik op een zone voor details."
msgstr ""
"Zone positions are an approximation based on the original plans\n"
"                            (LHOAS &amp; LHOAS architects) — not an architecturally exact trace.\n"
"                            Click a zone for details."
